text: Stipan Dora (8 April 1935 - 2002) was a Serbian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman bantamweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Serbian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Yugoslavia Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sombor
